  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Three fragments from a <rs type="decoration">tabella ansata</rs> (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.745</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.465</measure>) on a fluted <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">column</rs>; a (left side fragment) <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.30</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.30</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.14</measure>. b (centre fragment) <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.28</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.80</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.40</measure>. c (right lower corner) <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.27</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.36</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.29</measure>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> in tabella ansata.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Letters</head>
        <p>
          <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03-0.035</measure>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notBefore="0034" notAfter="0066" exact="none">Mid first century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
      </div>
